{"id": "1448988335640019007", "channel_id": "1448983774166651021", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "又沒有說這隊打遍天下無敵手，我只是說保證躺著過困難七，一個不用投資可以直接用的隊伍這麼礙著你了？", "timestamp": "2025-12-12T10:42:20.118000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-12T10:47:11.593000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448983774166651021", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全常駐，低配，無靈知，初見首通三星速通忘卻困難7——打擊轉反擊轉打擊：菲凱希帆血海打擊隊", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
